title: VA: Indie Electro Pop October 2013 - We Sink (Dutch Treat I3)
description:
Already the seventh and last playlist of the Indie Playlists October 2013. I could not make a 2-hour list so it became an 1-hour one...... Enjoy,

PS: All Dutch Treat Playlists keep the original tracks in tact and only adjust the time spaces (to the rhythm of the playlist). No mixing or what so ever.
